<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh a dawmi ra, Nan lawmhnak hngalhter tuah, Nannih dihlak hlasa cio
 u, Nannih dihlak hlasa cio u, Bawi thutdan pawngah cun, Bawi thutdan
 pawngah cun.

[C1]
   Zion khua kan kal lai, Zoh duh awk, aa dawh khua Zion Cunglei ah a
   ummi Zion, Pathian khua tha ah kan kal lai.

[V2]
 Pathian hngal lomi nih, Hlasak al hmanh hna seh, Vancung Bawibik fa
 hna nih cun, Vancung Bawibik fa hna nih cun, Hla cu an sak theo lai, Hla
 cu an sak theo lai.

[C2]
   Zion khua kan kal lai, Zoh duh awk, aa dawh khua Zion Cunglei ah a
   ummi Zion, Pathian khua tha ah kan kal lai.

[V3]
 Zion tlang cu a tha, Lawmhnak a tam a um, Vancung khua kha kan phak
 hlanah, Vancung khua kha kan phak hlanah, Kan hmuh nuamhnak a tam, Kan
 hmuh nuamhnak a tam.

[C3]
   Zion khua kan kal lai, Zoh duh awk, aa dawh khua Zion Cunglei ah a
   ummi Zion, Pathian khua tha ah kan kal lai.

[V4]
 Khi ca hlasa u si, mitthli kha a hul lai, Im-ma-nu-el ram in kan kal
 i, Im-ma-nu-el ram in kan kal i, Khua thabik kan phan lai, khua thabik
 kan phan lai.

[C4]
   Zion khua kan kal lai, Zoh duh awk, aa dawh khua Zion Cunglei ah a
   ummi Zion, Pathian khua tha ah kan kal lai.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>ZION KHUA AH KAN KAL LIO CH277</title>
</song>